{"tid":632576,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再用老屎忽口氣對待啲有情緒病或者感到挫敗嘅學生啦","createTime":"2018-04-17T13:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T15:15:02.000Z","uid":94075,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a3fc0e37192ae7841c53b7193903afc1e7c2bae","tid":632576,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T13:43:14.000Z","msg":"長文慎入<br />\n<br />\n見到有個po講 17歲絕望<br />\n下面一堆人係度懶係人生老屎忽咁講<br />\n&ldquo;第時出黎做野仲多野煩啦17歲絕咩望&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;00後垃撚圾&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n其實之前咁多學生自殺 都真係有版你睇 <br />\n咩年齡嘅人都好 都有佢地嘅難處 都有佢地嘅煩惱<br />\n但呢啲新聞一出黎 大部人嘅反應係<br />\n&ldquo;而家啲學生抗壓能力好低&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n無錯 學生時代係人生中最快樂嘅時候<br />\n但好似之前咁 咁短時間內有咁多單 <br />\n係咪應該要正視下係咩原因 <br />\n唔好只係識得有事死咗人先去關心下 <br />\n但啲學生想放下負就屌佢地冇用唔識面對<br />\n分分鐘係因為咁嘅風氣而唔敢講 <br />\n驚比人話冇用而收收埋埋<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家唔好再用啲老屎忽嘅心態<br />\n去對待向你求助嘅學生<br />\n每個人都有佢唔開心嘅權利 <br />\n唔係話年紀大啲先有權利抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n最後多謝睇哂呢篇文嘅巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14f16f0d3d2cc681312d3e0432825b799c8a8e9","tid":632576,"uid":133776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a3fc0e37192ae7841c53b7193903afc1e7c2bae","tid":632576,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T13:43:14.000Z","msg":"長文慎入<br />\n<br />\n見到有個po